Executive Assistant Company ICP Analysis and Pain
Point Statements
Executive Summary
This document provides a comprehensive analysis of the Ideal Customer Profile (ICP) for an
executive assistant company offering a four-week accelerator program that helps founders
rapidly build infrastructure in four key areas:
1. Email management
2. Calendar/time management
3. Personal/lifestyle management
4. Business process automation
The analysis includes:
-
-
-
Detailed categorization of ICP groups
Analysis of hopes, dreams, fears, and blockers for each group
25 refined pain point statements organized by service category
