Hopes, Dreams, Fears, and Blockers Analysis
Coaches
Hopes & Dreams
-
Building a sustainable coaching practice with consistent client flow
-
Spending more time on actual coaching rather than administrative tasks
-
Scaling their impact without sacrificing quality of service
-
Creating passive income streams through courses and programs
-
Establishing thought leadership in their niche
-
Maintaining work-life balance while growing their business
-
Commanding premium pricing for their expertise
-
Creating systems that allow for more freedom and flexibility
Fears & Blockers
-
-
-
-
-
-
-
-
-
