Overwhelm from wearing too many hats (coach, marketer, admin, etc.)
Email overload and missed opportunities
Calendar chaos and double-bookings
Inability to scale beyond trading time for money
Lack of systems and processes for efficient business operations
Difficulty prioritizing between client work and business development
Administrative tasks consuming creative energy
Burnout from handling everything themselves
